        <randlist type="bullet">
            <item>
                <para>The customer must provide a ground active momentary switch that is wired into the mid-chassis
                    connector.
                </para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>If the customer orders 60ABD but decides not to use an emergency pump, the customer should simply
                    use ICAP or the Diamond Logic&#8482; Builder software to enable software feature code 595245, and
                    remove software feature code 595246.
                </para>
            </item>
        </randlist>
        <figure id="f73000bf" figsize="pg-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg73/G73000BF.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="514px"
                     scalefitheight="432px"/>
